en_56432_0	The UNP today requested the government to conduct a complete and comprehensive investigation regarding the mass grave in Matale.
en_56432_1	General Secretary of the UNP MP Thissa Attanayaka made this statement while speaking at a press conference held in Colombo.
en_56432_2	The JVP also expressed their views regarding this at a press conference held yesterday.
en_56432_3	General Secretary of the JVP Tilvin Silva stated that the government would not be interested in conducting investigations regarding this mass grave which belonged to the period of the UNP government tenure.
